# Repository Structure — web_app

## Naming
- Directories: kebab-case (e.g., `components/auth-wizard`)
- Files: kebab-case (e.g., `user-card.tsx`, `use-user.ts`)
- Components: `PascalCase` function names with named exports

## Layout per feature
- Exported component at top of file; subcomponents follow
- Helpers next, static content after, interfaces/types at the end

```
src/
├── components/
│   └── auth-wizard/
│       ├── index.tsx
│       ├── subcomponents/
│       │   └── step-email.tsx
│       ├── helpers/
│       │   └── build-payload.ts
│       ├── static/
│       │   └── copy.ts
│       └── types.ts
├── services/
│   └── user-profile/
│       ├── client.ts
│       ├── queries.ts
│       └── types.ts
└── lib/
    ├── zod-schemas.ts
    ├── constants.ts
    └── types.ts
```

## Exports
- Prefer named exports; default exports discouraged
- Barrel files only at directory root (`index.ts`), not nested
